                <h2 class="section-sub-heading" id="live-text">Live text</h2>
                <p>working with live text is fundamental online. The days of text as image on websites is well in the past. Live text affords many basic benefits:</p>
                <p>Scalability. Live text can be resized to suit many presentational contexts.</p>
                <p>Searchability. Live text allows for search engines and other robots to parse content, making it easier to find, and more accessible to differently abled readers.</p>
                <p>Localizeability. Live text can be translated into multiple languages, thereby making worldwide distribution and delivery of comics a lot more accessible.</p>
                <p>Live text in comics can be achieved by using CSS to style caption boxes, word balloons, thought bubbles, and sound effects, in conjunction with SVG graphics to provide non standard shapes.</p>
